    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels at MRL 2. Six factors scoped to Gradation 1 and not assessed per MRL 2 requirements, consistent with ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1. CFD predictions of RH index satisfy the RH < 1 acceptance criterion at all 5 operating points with maximum discrepancy of 14.3%. Discretization uncertainty (GCI 3.2%) is within acceptable bounds. The model is deemed sufficiently credible to support the regulatory decision regarding worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
